{"ts": "2026-06-07T20:28:52.507652+00:00", "update": {"model": {"messages": [{"type": "ai", "data": {"content": "Now I have all the information needed. The `profiles.toml` file defines the encoding profiles shipped with `vidpack`.\n\n---\n\nWhen a user runs the `vidpack` command, they can select from **three** encoding profiles, each producing the following codec/container combination:\n\n| Profile | Video Codec | Audio Codec | Container |\n|---------|-------------|-------------|-----------|\n| **web** | `libx264` | `aac` | `.mp4` |\n| **archive** | `libx265` | `flac` | `.mkv` |\n| **gif** | *(none – animated image)* | *(none)* | `.gif` |\n\nHere's a closer look at each:\n\n1. **`web`** — Encodes video with **H.264** (`libx264`) and audio with **AAC**, muxed into an **MP4** container. It scales to 1280×720 and targets a 2 Mbit/s video bitrate.\n\n2. **`archive`** — Encodes video with **H.265/HEVC** (`libx265`) and audio with **FLAC** (lossless), muxed into an **MKV** (Matroska) container. It uses CRF 18 (high quality) and keeps the source resolution.\n\n3. **`gif`** — Produces an **animated GIF** (no separate audio/video codecs). It runs at 12 fps and scales the width to 480 px (height auto-calculated). The file notes this uses a single-pass palette generation, which is a known quality limitation.\n\nThe profiles are defined in the `profiles.toml` file and are fully user-customizable; profile names must be lowercase ASCII.", "additional_kwargs": {"refusal": null}, "response_metadata": {"token_usage": {"completion_tokens": 405, "prompt_tokens": 4314, "total_tokens": 4719, "completion_tokens_details": {"accepted_prediction_tokens": null, "audio_tokens": 0, "reasoning_tokens": 28, "rejected_prediction_tokens": null, "image_tokens": 0}, "prompt_tokens_details": {"audio_tokens": 0, "cached_tokens": 3456, "cache_write_tokens": 0, "video_tokens": 0}, "cost": 0, "is_byok": true, "cost_details": {"upstream_inference_cost": 0.0007380216, "upstream_inference_prompt_cost": 0.0003856716, "upstream_inference_completions_cost": 0.00035235}}, "model_provider": "openai", "model_name": "xiaomi/mimo-v2.5-pro-20260422", "system_fingerprint": null, "id": "gen-1780864124-ssd4z7WXoz9QCUaHeeh6", "finish_reason": "stop", "logprobs": null}, "type": "ai", "name": null, "id": "lc_run--019ea3c6-042e-7a51-a874-09cbec4e07d4-0", "tool_calls": [], "invalid_tool_calls": [], "usage_metadata": {"input_tokens": 4314, "output_tokens": 405, "total_tokens": 4719, "input_token_details": {"audio": 0, "cache_read": 3456}, "output_token_details": {"audio": 0, "reasoning": 28}}}}]}}}
